      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/nse-mrl5-gradation4",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error (iterative convergence, round-off, and solver-specific artifacts) was flagged as an epistemic gap. Residual convergence criteria were applied but solver error was not formally bounded. Not assessed at MRL 5 requirements; achieved level defaults to Gradation 1."
