    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package for test-harness purposes under the condition that open gaps are tracked as action items. Notably, the Discretization Error and Relevance of Quantities of Interest factors carry requiredLevel declarations without linked acceptanceCriteria records, constituting the targeted W-AR-01 weakness. The structured basis for those required gradations is absent from the package; only narrative rationale is present.",
